User Stories for "Clean and Simple Design" Epic:

As a website visitor, I want to be able to navigate the website easily and find what I am looking for without getting confused by the layout or design.
As a website administrator, I want to ensure that the website has a consistent color scheme, typography, and layout throughout all pages to maintain a professional and cohesive look and feel.
As a website visitor, I want to be able to access the website from any device (desktop, mobile, tablet) and have the design be responsive to the device's screen size and resolution.
